    <id>https://lnx1usr.top/2023/09/19/markdown%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B/</id>
    <published>2023-09-19T14:30:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-09-19T15:46:22.547Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>空行划段井标题，前加大号是引句。<br>    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#标题一号</span><br><span class="line">##标题二号 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">###标题三号</span><br><span class="line">&gt;该语句是表示引用的句子。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>两星下斜四星粗，四波浪线加删除。<br>    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*斜体* _斜体_</span><br><span class="line">**粗体** __粗体__</span><br><span class="line">~~已加删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>    输出为：<br>    <em>斜体</em> <em>斜体</em><br>    <strong>粗体</strong> <strong>粗体</strong><br>    <del>已加删除线</del></p><p>表格简用横和竖，再用冒号表对齐。</p><p>abcd|cdef|fghr|arrsdf|yyruue|aasrsd<br>-|-|-|:-:|-:|:-<br>1|20|10|A|b|c<br>输出为：</p><table><thead><tr><th>abcd</th><th>cdef</th><th>fghr</th><th align="center">arrsdf</th><th align="right">yyruue</th><th align="left">aasrsd</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>20</td><td>10</td><td align="center">A</td><td align="right">b</td><td align="left">c</td></tr><tr><td>不知道哪里的问题，居中：没正确显示。</td><td></td><td></td><td align="center"></td><td align="right"></td><td align="left"></td></tr></tbody></table><p>星或下线开无序，有序自是数字起。</p><pre><code>*无序第一行*无序第二行-无序第一行-无序第二行1.有序第一行2.有序第二行</code></pre><p>嵌套列表俩空格，组合使用更清楚。</p><pre><code>1.嵌套有序第一组  *嵌套无序第一行  *嵌套无序第二行 2.嵌套有序第二组   -嵌套无序第一行   -嵌套无序第二行</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
